== 2019-04-19 version 1.0.0

* ignore Gemfile.lock [#178](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/178)
* fix sqlite type conversion warnings [#176](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/176)
* fix Dangerous query method warnings [#175](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/175)
* Drop somve dependency
  * coffee-rails [#170](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/170)
  * slim-rails [#171](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/171)
* Drop support under Rails5.1 [#169](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/169)

