== 2018-08-09 version 0.4.0

* refactor execution failure handling [#160](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/160)
* add new storage type cache [#162](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/162)
* refactor ConnectionWrapper for connection scope [#161](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/161)
* fix N+1 queries for adhoq_reports [#158](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/158)
* add `hide_rows_count` configuration [#157](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/157)
* drop support below ruby 2.3 [#159](https://github.com/esminc/adhoq/pull/159)

